    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 296
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Ena",
      "Body": "'This time, too, when I tried to draw what I felt after listening to K's song, it just flowed smoothly.'",
